Calming the Breath
Comes in five stages:
Following the Breath;
Guarding the breath at a certain point;
Giving rise to an imaginary image at that guarding point;
*7-8 months later I return after I have gathered the necessary experience. So that we can talk experience-to-experience, not just experience-to-words.
Manipulating those images in any ways that we want in order to gain power over them;
Selecting one of these images and contemplating it in a most concentrated way until the breath becomes truly calm and peaceful.
